originalText.text: If I could give her zero stars I would. Unprofessional, unresponsive, no compassion and shows that she truly doesn’t care about the health of her patients. My mother is very mentally ill and was not ready to be discharged (as she told Ms Perry) and was discharged anyway. Perry proceeded to tell my mother that if no one picked her up that she would be charged $1000 and told her she would send her home even if no one came to get her. All while knowing that my mother felt extremely unsafe for her life.
